{
  "stem": "25938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the only-- the only little town, shtetl, that I know of with a Jewish minority.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In other little towns around Porzecze, the-- the-- the shtetlekh consisted of Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Most of them, the Jews were in the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The non-Jews lived outside the town, the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But there was one-- one little town, Sidra, where I was teaching, that it was like a Jewish-- like-- like-- like-- I felt like I was in a Jewish land.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were only Jews there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Only once a week they used to come to the market, the peasants, to sell things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But otherwise, we were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were used to-- to-- to-- to work down the streets about 11 o'clock, 10 o'clock at night, and only Jews were there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was actually an autonomy, in a way, in a culture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Even in-- Grodno, in a big town, where gymnasiums, Jewish places, everything was in Hebrew, the schools.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, I was teaching privately, even in my little town too, privately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have formal education as a teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you asked about [NON-ENGLISH], about future, we didn't think in these terms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now I'm-- I'm-- I'm reliving that-- that fear, what would I do if I grew up later?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have any-- any profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, but when the Soviets came, I became a teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in 1938, I-- I was working in a little-- in that Sidra, in that-- that little town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came in the year 1939, the service took over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was in my little town already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- and then they opened classes for-- for people who wanted to be teachers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I graduated from my class in six months, a very intensive class.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
